data.description: If you're looking for a well-sized condo, in an amenity rich community, this is it! This stylish second floor unit features Luxury Vinyl Tiling throughout the main rooms. The great room has plenty of space, an attached formal dining area and opens to the kitchen. Enhanced with custom moldings, the kitchen offers plenty of cabinets and counter space.  The sliders in the living room open to the balcony, bringing loads of natural light to this home. The second bedroom is currently being used as a den and is a well-sized room. The main bedroom offers an en-suite bathroom and large walk-in closet. An additional full bath is in the hallway for guests to use. Windows and slider were replaced along with water heater.  There is a keyed storage closet located right outside this home for your additional items. Outdoor pools, tennis, gym, party room and many more amenities all available for your enjoyment. Conveniently located near shops, restaurants, and public transportation.
